title: Can Anyone Beat the Chiefs?
description:
Cole and Ryan are joined by The Ringer’s Kaelen Jones, and they start by talking about the Baltimore Ravens' shoot-out victory against the Cleveland Browns (2:00). Then they talk about how to improve the Pittsburgh Steelers now that they’ve lost two in a row(12:30). And are there any teams that can challenge the Kansas City Chiefs (27:10)?

Hosts: Ryan Shazier and Cole Wright
Guest: Kaelen Jones
